"      <tr class=\"divider_top\">",
"       <td>",
"        Conversion from oral tablets",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        1 mg of oral daily &asymp; 1.25 mg LAI every 3 weeks",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        Initiate LAI at 10 to 20 times daily oral dose, up to 100 mg. If initial conversion requires &gt;100 mg, follow by balance in 3 to 7 days. Then administer at 4 week intervals.",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        Initiate LAI at 25 mg every 2 weeks. For first 3 weeks overlap with full-dose oral treatment.",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        Conversion from oral extended release: if stable on oral 12 mg daily, then 234 mg LAI; if 6 mg oral daily, then 117 mg LAI; if 3 mg oral daily, then 39 to 78 mg LAI",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        <p>",
"         If stable on oral 10 mg daily, then 210 mg LAI every 2 weeks or 405 mg LAI every 4 weeks for first 8 weeks, then 150 mg IM LAI every 2 weeks or 300 mg every 4 weeks",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         If stable on oral 15 mg daily, then 300 mg LAI every 2 weeks for first 8 weeks, then 210 mg LAI every 2 weeks or 405 mg LAI every 4 weeks",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         If stable on oral 20 mg daily then 300 mg LAI every 2 weeks",
"        </p>",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        <p>",
"         Initiate LAI at 4 times daily oral dose every two weeks or 8 times daily oral dose every 4 weeks. For first week, overlap with oral treatment.",
"        </p>",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        <p>",
"         If stable on oral dose up to 20 mg daily then 100 mg LAI every 2 weeks",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         If stable on 25 to 40 mg oral daily, then 200 mg LAI every 2 weeks",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         If stable on 50 to 75 mg oral daily then 300 mg LAI every 2 weeks",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         If stable on more than 75 mg daily then 400 mg LAI every 2 weeks",
"        </p>",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        Discontinue oral treatment. Initiate at 50 to 100 mg LAI every 3 weeks. Individualize dose and interval in 25 mg increments based on response no more frequently than every 2 to 3 weeks.",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
